        produce the most raw power but require acreage and higher upfront cost. For maximum efficiency,
        pair a <span class="rec-highlight">Wind Spindle + Solar</span> hybrid system — today's simulation shows
        that combination covers <span class="rec-highlight" id="recCoverage">—%</span> of a typical home's daily needs.
